--[2022-10-11 00:07:18] Entity Properties
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then case when i.data_space_id > 0 then i.data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075850725,  case ds.type when 'FG' then case when t.lob_data_space_id > 0 then t.lob_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075850685,  t.lock_on_bulk_load,
       1075838979,    1075850726,  t.text_in_row_limit,
       1075838979,    1075850684,  t.large_value_types_out_of_row,
       1075838979,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075851024,  case when ctt.object_id IS NOT NULL then 1 else 0 end,
       1075838979,    1075851053,  t.lock_escalation_desc,
       1075838979,    1075851222,  case when ctt.object_id IS NOT NULL then case ctt.is_track_columns_updated_on when 1 then 'ON' else 'OFF' end end,
       1075838979,    1075850882,  case objectproperty(t.object_id, 'TableHasVarDecimalStorageFormat') when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838979,    1075852284,  case when t.is_memory_optimized = 1 then 1 when t.is_filetable = 1 then 2 else 0 end,
       1075838979,    1075852294,  ft.directory_name,
       1075838979,    1075852295,  ft.filename_collation_name,
       1075838979,    1075852285,  case t.durability when 1 then 0 else 1 end 
FROM sys.tables t 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.indexes i on t.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id in (0, 1) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.change_tracking_tables ctt on ctt.object_id = t.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.filetables ft on t.object_id = ft.object_id 
WHERE t.object_id = 1275151588 AND t.is_external=0 AND t.temporal_type <> 1
--Parameter 1 = 1275151588
--[2022-10-11 00:07:18] Return from Query - 0 rows


--[2022-10-11 00:07:18] Entity ExternalTableProperties
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075853373,  et.location,
       1075838979,    1075853375,  ed.name,
       1075838979,    1075853395,  ef.name,
       1075838979,    1075853402,  case when et.reject_type = 'VALUE' then 0 when et.reject_type = 'PERCENTAGE' then 1 else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075853377,  et.reject_value,
       1075838979,    1075853378,  CAST(et.reject_sample_value AS int),
       1075838979,    1075850602,  t.Is_External 
FROM sys.tables t 
LEFT OUTER JOIN  sys.external_tables et on et.object_id = t.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.external_data_sources ed on et.data_source_id = ed.data_source_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN  sys.external_file_formats ef on ef.file_format_id=et.file_format_id

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1339151816

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1307151702
--Parameter 1 = 1307151702

FROM sys.tables t

       1075839020,    1075848986,  case when cc.definition <> '' then cc.definition else sm.definition end,
       1075839020,    1075852160,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cast ( 0 as bit ) else cast ( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075839169,    1073742126,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then o.name else '%ColumnCheckConstraintName' end,
       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,
       1075839169,    1075849722,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 end,
       1075839169,    1075849061,  o.object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 1355151873 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1355151873

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1957582012 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075838979,    1075852294,  ft.directory_name,

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 2037582297

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 402100473 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 482100758

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,

       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,

FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id

       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1413580074

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 82099333

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1461580245 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 2053582354

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,

       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

--[2022-10-11 00:07:24] Entity DataCompression
IF exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 2133582639 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN if exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 2133582639 and partition_number > 1 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 2133582639 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 802101898

--[2022-10-11 00:07:24] Entity PartitionColumns
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,
       1075839261,    1075851246,  ic.partition_ordinal,
       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id) 
FROM sys.tables t

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partition_schemes ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.index_columns ic on t.object_id = ic.object_id and (ic.index_id = 0 or i.type = 1) and partition_ordinal > 0

       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 802101898 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 802101898 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 802101898 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 802101898 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 802101898) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 802101898 END END END

--[2022-10-11 00:07:24] Entity ColumnStoreIndex
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075839338,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075839338,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075839338,    1075850519,  case i.type when 5 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839338,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075839338,    1075849143,  i.filter_definition,
       1075839338,    1075852470,  i.compression_delay,
       1075839338,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
WHERE (i.type = 5 OR i.type = 6) AND i.object_id = 802101898

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1010102639
--Parameter 1 = 1010102639

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075849004,  case i.is_unique when 1 then 'AK' else 'IE' end,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 366624349 
ORDER BY i.index_id

--[2022-10-11 00:07:25] Entity DataCompression
IF exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 366624349 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN if exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 366624349 and partition_number > 1 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 366624349 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 366624349 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 366624349 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 366624349 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 366624349) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 366624349 END END END

       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1653580929

--[2022-10-11 00:07:26] Entity PrimaryKeyIndex
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 510624862 
ORDER BY i.index_id

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 2018106230
--Parameter 1 = 2018106230

--[2022-10-11 00:07:28] Entity TemporalProperties
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075852336,  case t.temporal_type when 0 then cast( 0 as bit ) else cast( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075838979,    1075852337,  '[' + s.name + '].[' + ht.name + ']',
       1075838979,    1075852338,  case c.generated_always_type when 1 then c.name else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075852339,  case c.generated_always_type when 2 then c.name else NULL end 
FROM sys.tables t

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075849004,  case i.is_unique when 1 then 'AK' else 'IE' end,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1154103152 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,

       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,

       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.uses_native_compilation = 1 then 'TM' else tr.type end,

       1075839021,    1075850711,  sm.is_schema_bound 
FROM sys.triggers tr

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 1154103152

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 178099675

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1749581271
--Parameter 1 = 1749581271

FROM sys.tables t

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1301579675

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1301579675

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1365579903

FROM sys.tables t

       1075839020,    1075848986,  case when cc.definition <> '' then cc.definition else sm.definition end,
       1075839020,    1075852160,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cast ( 0 as bit ) else cast ( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075839169,    1073742126,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then o.name else '%ColumnCheckConstraintName' end,
       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,
       1075839169,    1075849722,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 end,
       1075839169,    1075849061,  o.object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 1826105546 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075839020,    1075850737,  SCHEMA_NAME(o.schema_id),
       1075839020,    1075848986,  case when cc.definition <> '' then cc.definition else sm.definition end,
       1075839020,    1075852160,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cast ( 0 as bit ) else cast ( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075839169,    1073742126,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then o.name else '%ColumnCheckConstraintName' end,
       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,
       1075839169,    1075849722,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 end,
       1075839169,    1075849061,  o.object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 386100416 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 386100416
--Parameter 1 = 386100416

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 386100416

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 274100017
